{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:31:13.503282+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: a0792bb3a5f4cb9f4a3c7df405a950368ed26fcd)", "id": "lc_10507b31-2727-48c8-9a29-acf7d37c2fb1"}, {"type": "text", "text": "import React, { useState } from 'react';\nimport { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom';\nimport { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';\nimport DashboardNavbar from '@/layouts/dashboard/DashboardNavbar';\nimport DashboardSidebar from '@/layouts/dashboard/DashboardSidebar';\n\nconst APP_BAR_MOBILE = 64;\nconst APP_BAR_DESKTOP = 92;\n\nconst RootStyle = styled('div')({\n    display: 'flex',\n    minHeight: '100%',\n    overflow: 'hidden'\n});\n\nconst MainStyle = styled('div')(({ theme }) => ({\n    flexGrow: 1,\n    overflow: 'auto',\n    minHeight: '100%',\n    paddingTop: APP_BAR_MOBILE + 24,\n    paddingBottom: theme.spacing(10),\n    [theme.breakpoints.up('lg')]: {\n        paddingTop: APP_BAR_DESKTOP + 24,\n        paddingLeft: theme.spacing(2),\n        paddingRight: theme.spacing(2)\n    }\n}));\n\nconst DashboardLayout = () => {\n    const [open, setOpen] = useState(false);\n\n    return (\n        <RootStyle>\n            <DashboardNavbar onOpenSidebar={() => setOpen(true)} />\n            <DashboardSidebar isOpenSidebar={open} onCloseSidebar={() => setOpen(false)} />\n            <MainStyle>\n                <Outlet />\n            </MainStyle>\n        </RootStyle>\n    );\n};\n\nexport default DashboardLayout;\n", "id": "lc_63caa3ad-a8a1-4559-b9df-de1c2eb5d598"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "015f19fe-73a8-4a4b-b1d7-6acc23bc9169", "tool_call_id": "call_644d670deb8742289dc2f3c3", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:31:28.167634+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's how routing is organized in this React admin app:\n\n---\n\n## Routing Architecture\n\n### Entry Point (`src/main.tsx`)\n\nThe app bootstraps with `BrowserRouter` from React Router, wrapped in a `HelmetProvider` (for `<head>` management) and a `ThemeConfig` (MUI theming). A `ScrollToTop` component resets scroll position on navigation. The `<Router />` component (from `src/routes.tsx`) renders the full route tree.\n\n### Route Tree (`src/routes.tsx`)\n\nAll routing is defined in a single file using React Router v6's `<Routes>` / `<Route>` API. There are **two top-level layout groups**:\n\n#### 1. `/dashboard` — the admin shell (`DashboardLayout`)\n\n```\n/dashboard        → Redirects (Navigate) to /dashboard/app\n/dashboard/app    → DashboardApp page\n/dashboard/user   → User page\n/dashboard/products → Products page\n/dashboard/blog   → Blog page\n```\n\n`DashboardLayout` (`src/layouts/dashboard/index.tsx`) is a classic admin panel structure:\n- **`DashboardNavbar`** — top app bar (mobile-friendly hamburger toggle)\n- **`DashboardSidebar`** — collapsible side navigation with links driven by `SidebarConfig.tsx`\n- **`<Outlet />`** — renders the matched child page\n\nThe sidebar has an `open` state managed locally, toggled from the navbar and closed via the sidebar's own close handler. This layout is always visible for any `/dashboard/*` route.\n\n#### 2. `/` — the lightweight shell (`LogoOnlyLayout`)\n\n```\n/login            → Login page\n/register         → Register page\n/404              → NotFound (Page404) page\n/                 → Redirects to /dashboard\n*  (catch-all)    → Redirects to /404\n```\n\n`LogoOnlyLayout` (`src/layouts/LogoOnlyLayout.tsx`) is a minimal shell — just a logo in a fixed-position header and an `<Outlet />` for child content. It's used for auth pages and the 404 page.\n\n### Redirects Summary\n\n| Trigger | Behavior |\n|---|---|\n| `/` (root) | `Navigate` → `/dashboard` |\n| `/dashboard` (bare) | `Navigate` → `/dashboard/app` |\n| `*` (any unmatched URL) | `Navigate` → `/404` |\n\n### 404 / Fallback Behavior\n\nThe catch-all wildcard `path=\"*\"` lives inside the `LogoOnlyLayout` group. It redirects (via `<Navigate to=\"/404\" />`) to the explicit `/404` route, which renders the `NotFound` component (`src/pages/Page404.tsx`). So the 404 page is displayed within the `LogoOnlyLayout` shell (logo header, no sidebar/navbar chrome).\n\n### Auth-Related Pages\n\n`Login` and `Register` are **not** protected by any route guard or auth wrapper. They render inside `LogoOnlyLayout` alongside the 404 page. Note that an `AuthLayout.tsx` exists in `src/layouts/` but is **not referenced** in the route tree — it appears to be unused (or reserved for future use).\n\n### Visual Summary\n\n```\n<BrowserRouter>\n  <Routes>\n    ├── /dashboard ──── DashboardLayout (sidebar + navbar + <Outlet/>)\n    │   ├── \"\"         → Redirect → /dashboard/app\n    │   ├── app        → DashboardApp\n    │   ├── user       → User\n    │   ├── products   → Products\n    │   └── blog       → Blog\n    │\n    └── / ──────────── LogoOnlyLayout (logo + <Outlet/>)\n        ├── login      → Login\n        ├── register   → Register\n        ├── 404        → NotFound\n        ├── \"\"         → Redirect → /dashboard\n        └── *          → Redirect → /404\n```\n\nThe design is straightforward: all \"admin\" pages live under `/dashboard` with a persistent sidebar/nav chrome, while unauthenticated or unknown pages use a minimal logo-only shell. Route-level code splitting (e.g., `React.lazy`) is **not** used — all page components are eagerly imported.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1313, "prompt_tokens": 15442, "total_tokens": 16755, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 409, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 15040, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000466032, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 9.8392e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00036764}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871473-kN9bKuCan3QCFs4IuxA0", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea436-2960-7123-a678-a57c51e626da-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 15442, "output_tokens": 1313, "total_tokens": 16755, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 15040}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 409}}}}]}}}
